This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for extracting financial and economic events from text. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) techniques.
